# main-no-module-no-api

[![NPM version][npm-image]][npm-url]

> A module with main but no module nor api info

## Installation

Install `main-no-module-no-api` using [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/):

```bash
npm install --save main-no-module-no-api
```
